<div class="answer-head">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$zengjuchen"
class="zm-item-link-avatar"
href="/people/zengjuchen">
<img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/5acfa84d9_s.jpg"
class="zm-list-avatar"
data-source="http://pic2.zhimg.com/5acfa84d9_s.jpg" />
</a>



<a data-tip="p$t$zengjuchen" href="/people/zengjuchen">曾举臣</a>，<strong title="世界和我想的不一样" class="zu-question-my-bio">世界和我想的不一样</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="3">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$xiao-yan-90-70" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/xiao-yan-90-70" class="zg-link" title="xiao yan">xiao yan</a>、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户</span>
</span>


<span>赞同</span>


</div>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="905044" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix">你需要的是<b>3M6200面罩 + 6005滤盒，</b> 如果从没买过，直接买七件套，一般商家也是这样搭配卖的。<br><br>装修最常见的气体污染物是甲苯，二甲苯，甲醛。 前两者主要来自油漆，后者来自粘合剂及其他（具体情况请自行wikipedia).<br><br>具体的商家，京东，亚马逊，天猫都有。我自己从天猫上买的，比京东和亚马逊便宜50元钱。<br><br>以上为自己今晚搜索学习所得到的信息，因为楼下某公司使用劣质装修材料，已经快被熏晕了。<br><br>ps: 附图为3m各种类滤盒所针对防护的污染气体<br><br><noscript><img src="http://pic4.zhimg.com/4dd5b7f0eeda397018e0f228897b4a07_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="684" data-rawheight="870" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="684" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/4dd5b7f0eeda397018e0f228897b4a07_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="684" data-rawheight="870" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="684" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/4dd5b7f0eeda397018e0f228897b4a07_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic4.zhimg.com/4dd5b7f0eeda397018e0f228897b4a07_b.jpg">


</div>

</div>
